<h1>Welcome to the Solar System</h1>

<img src="/images/solar-system.webp" class="img-fluid rounded mb-3" alt="The solar system">

<p>The solar system is made up of the Sun, eight planets, moons, asteroids, comets, and many other objects in space.</p>
<p>This website introduces some of the most interesting parts of our solar system in a simple and creative way.</p>
<p>You can explore the inner planets, learn about the outer planets, and read about why the solar system is such an important topic in astronomy.</p>
<p>The solar system is fascinating because every planet is unique and helps us understand more about the universe.</p>
<p>I chose this topic because I am very interested in space and astronomy.</p>

<p>Image source: <a href="https://solarsystem.nasa.gov/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">NASA Solar System Exploration</a></p>

